28/09/2007
ATHENS, Greece -- Parliament chose Dimitris Sioufas as its new speaker Thursday (September 27th). He had served as development minister in the previous cabinet. In his address to parliament, Sioufas vowed to be professional and impartial, and promised to step up international parliamentary co-operation and develop annual Youth Parliament projects. (ANA-MPA, NET - 27/09/07)
